quran[7]{c,v,t}:
  11,82,"Nde yamiroore Amen halkugol yim…ďe Luutu …ďen arunoo, Men wa…ótiri dow saare ma…ď…ďe nden ley mayre e hoore ma…ď…ďe. Men saa∆īini e ma…ď…ďe kaa∆īe iwru…óe e loope joor…óe fawondire."
  11,83,"∆äe kaa∆īe no maandiniraa ka Joomi maa…óa maande heeriinde. ∆äen kaa∆īe wonaali wo…ó…óu…óe e too√Īoo…ďe qurayshi …ďen e wo…ó…ďe goo. ∆äen no hebilii tuma kala Alla hoddiri jippingol …óe e ma…ď…ďe, …óe jippoo."
  11,84,"Men Nulii kadi e Madyana'en musi…ó…óo makko on Shu'aybu, o m maaki: Ko onon yo yim…ďe am, rewee Alla tun. Rewetee…óo haandu…óo e dewal alanaa on ko woori Mo. Wata on …óuytu …ďetu ngun e manndake …óen tuma etanton yim…ďe …ďen. Min on mi…óo yi'i on e yaajraa…ďe arsike e neema. Wata on wa…ótitir neema Alla on e moo…óon geddi. Min non mi…óo hulani on lepte √Īalaande fiiltotoonde kala gooto e mo'on, on he…ďataa ka dogiri wanaa ka faabo…óon."
  11,85,"Ko onon yo yim…ďe am, hunniree …ďetu ngun e manndake …óen nun…óal tuma etanton wo…ó…ďe goo. Wata on …óuytiran yim…ďe …ďen huunde e haqqeeji ma…ď…ďe …óin hodo e janfa, wata on bonnir ka leydi warugol e geddi ko wonaa …óum."
  11,86,"Ko keddiide Alla …óe O accani on …óen e kon ko daganii on …ďaawo jonnitirgol yim…ďe …ďen haqqeeji ma…ď…ďe …óin, …ďuri wondannde on e nafa diini …ďeydaari he…ďorayndi ndin …óuytugol …ďetu maa bonnugol ka leydi. Si on laatike gom…óim…ďe ka goonga. Si on laatike gom…óim…ďe, yarlitoree …óen kedde Alla …óon. Min on mi wonaali reenoowo on e golle mon, sakko mi hasba on e majje. Reenoowo on e …óum, ko O anndu…óo ko suu…óii e ko ."
  11,87,"Yim…ďe Shu'aybu …ďen wi'ani mo: Ko an yo Shuaybu! E ko julde maa nde juulataa nden fii Alla yamir-maa nde men accata rewugol ko baabiraa…ďe amen …ďen rewaynoo kon e sanamu, maa nde men accata wa…óugol e jawle amen …óen ko men yi…ói, men …ďeydira …óen no men yi…óiri? Pellet an ko a mu√Ī√Īii…óo feewu…óo. An oo haqqil…óo √Īee√Īo no men anndirno-maa ado nduu noddaandu maa, ko he…ďu-maa?"
  11,88,"Shu'aybu maakani yim…ďe makko …ďen: Ko onon yo yim…ďe am, yeetee lam: si tawii ko e …ďanngannduyee immorde ka Joomi am won-mi, O arsikii lam immorde ka Makko arsike dagii…óo, wano Annabaaku ngun?... Mi faandaaki ha…óugol on huunde, mi lunndoo on e wa…óugol nde. Mi faandaaki e noddaandu am ndun si wanaa mo∆ī∆īingol bajjinnde Joomi mon …óoftoo Mo yeru ko waaw-mi. Hawrinneede am e …óum ko ka Alla Senii…óo On. Ko e Makko tun mi fawi denndaangal fiyakuuji am, ko ka Makko kadi woni ruttorde am."